{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "ddd04fae-a7f8-473e-999f-8b43dfbdfa85",
    "name": "PMS Backend API Postman Documentations",
    "description": "Koleksi endpoint untuk menguji Boilerplate Autentikasi berbasis Moleculer JS.\n\n**Cara pakai:**\n1. Jalankan server: `npm run dev`\n2. Eksekusi **2. User Login** terlebih dahulu — access token dan refresh token akan otomatis tersimpan ke env variable `jwt_token` dan `refresh_token`\n3. Semua request protected sudah terkonfigurasi menggunakan `{{jwt_token}}`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "28256932",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/28256932-ddd04fae-a7f8-473e-999f-8b43dfbdfa85?source=collection_link"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth Service",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. User Registration",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"admin\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123\",\n    \"email\": \"admin@gmail.com\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "register"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Mendaftarkan pengguna baru ke sistem."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. User Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData && jsonData.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"refresh_token\", jsonData.refreshToken);",
                  "    console.log(\"Tokens automatically saved to environment variables!\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {},
                "requests": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"admin@gmail.com\",\n    \"password\": \"admin123\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "login"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Login dan dapatkan JWT Access Token & Refresh Token.\n\n*Catatan: Script Postman pada endpoint ini telah dikonfigurasi untuk menangkap nilai token balasan secara otomatis dan memindahkannya ke Environment Variable `jwt_token` dan `refresh_token`. Anda tinggal mengeksekusi request berikutnya tanpa perlu copy-paste token manual!*"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Get My Profile (Protected)",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/me",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "me"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Endpoint yang terotorisasi. Hanya pengguna yang menyematkan `Bearer Token` di bagian HTTP header (Authorization) yang dapat mengakses ini. Token tersebut diambil otomatis dari hasil login."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData && jsonData.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log(\"New Access Token automatically saved!\");",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "packages": {},
                "requests": {}
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"refreshToken\": \"854c12f4b53309ba883717668806af8aaee81b6ab8fbe5031b55c10360b5d6180a5cd2b070b1bc32de27de876dbc4723f30915c94db9902840fc34c17f084d3a\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/refresh",
              "host": [
                "{{base_url}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "refresh"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Memperbarui Access Token yang sudah expired menggunakan Refresh Token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"refreshToken\": \"12803f3cee4df8a0b917a38b3fd2c4ebc93dcee5c7eaa0ac9d9f6d91c6a3abc958dc160d1b879496af9619bfca469d77c30db30522f2176c2a1f6c55553acf2e\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
